{"tid":2422377,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬雲唔見人！李嘉誠重奪福布斯香港富豪榜首位","createTime":"2021-02-25T06:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T09:35:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f68db67a6a19614f04a2fa0c62ef3614aa7ed275","tid":2422377,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577422-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577422-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFWztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=9367415b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577422-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e9ed047c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577422-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n福布斯公布最新香港富豪榜，長和創辦人李嘉誠以354億美元財富，再度成為香港首富，整體財富增長20%，受惠於其持股的Zoom帶來的增長，抵銷長實集團股價下挫27%的影響。<br />\n<br />\n三甲亦包括恒地創辦人李兆基及新世界主席鄭家純，兩者分別以305億美元和221億美元，排行第2及第3。<br />\n<br />\n至於手機玻璃製造商伯恩光學的楊建文和林惠英，以186億美元排名第4，智能電話屏幕玻璃需求增長，帶動其財富增長逾1倍。<br />\n<br />\n其餘排名首10位的本港富豪，包括銀河娛樂主席呂志和、李錦記主席李文達、九倉大股東吳光正、華人置業創辦人劉鑾雄、新地鄺肖卿，以及阿里巴巴副主席蔡崇信。<br />\n<br />\n福布斯指，雖然香港去年經濟收縮6.1%，但股市造好，帶動香港首50名富豪的財富，增長7.5%至3310億美元。"},{"pid":"fb464c2ea9d7a0fb24f5245b5fd664c6e5ef5fb6","tid":2422377,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50c4858a9b57491017c25d4a0d59cc10357705e","tid":2422377,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:57:41.000Z","msg":"香港富豪榜？"},{"pid":"62e7b3279d90dee1cdb2ddb48081ca398965bbad","tid":2422377,"uid":223816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f50c4858a9b57491017c25d4a0d59cc10357705e","tid":2422377,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:57:41.000Z","msg":"香港富豪榜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:58:40.000Z","msg":"香港身份證富豪榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7387e90dc92879a57aa9673c387652f4ef1fdea2","tid":2422377,"uid":60307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"網隊老細都算香港人？"},{"pid":"ecf720b091f396b316981b0f3abab11f03a22083","tid":2422377,"uid":61589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:00:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20131022000452-260108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fnewspapers%2F20131022000452-260108&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFWztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=cf7a0808\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20131022000452-260108</a><br />\n<blockquote>馬雲：李嘉誠時代已過去 <span class=\"red\">2013/10/22</span><br />\n言談間，馬雲表示，時代已經不同，昔日的遊戲規則及行業生態已經完全改變，要保持創新才能迎合新世代的轉變。談到李嘉誠，他說：「李嘉誠在他那個時代，真的很不錯，但現在已不可能出現另一個李嘉誠。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+x哥：<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c021a1c0a4554f09639b9da1711bb5048ccda6a","tid":2422377,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"華人置業創辦人劉鑾雄<br />\n搞笑？"},{"pid":"54db622854a4d960b5705534acc5d8002c53dbbb","tid":2422377,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"有錢人嘅鬥爭比窮人更心狠手辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77297b947cc18763b05d9570ae709373003ffa2c","tid":2422377,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c021a1c0a4554f09639b9da1711bb5048ccda6a","tid":2422377,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"華人置業創辦人劉鑾雄<br />\n搞笑？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTim